text: Kazi Khademul Islam () (31 January 1925 – 28 March 1990) is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Jessore-1. ==Career== Islam was elected to parliament from Jessore-1 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:1925 births Category:1990 deaths Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members
title: Kazi Khademul Islam
